#: ../../source/manual/how-tos/ipsec-rw-w7.rst:50
msgid ""
"On tab **Networking** in IPv4 configuration under **Advanced** is the "
"option **Use defaut gateway on remote network**. If this option is "
"enabled, all traffic will be sent through the VPN (if IPsec SA matches). "
"When unchecked, you have to set specific routes sent via VPN."
msgstr ""

